messages.speech: There are no on-spot registrations. Please ensure you have completed your GHCI 18 registrations online prior to the conference. During the on-site registrations delegates can pick up their attendee badge. GHCI 18 attendee bags will be only given out on November 14, 2018. How else can I help you?
